insertNode(int, int, String) - Method in class Node
Method used to insert Node into the binary Tree Works by detecting whether the ID passed in is bigger than, smaller than or larger than the ID of the current Node, it then uses recursion to loop through until it finds a null node and then sets up the node with the relevant information
